Add ADDA Device Audio Interface support for MT8365 SoC.

Reviewed-by: AngeloGioacchino Del Regno <angelogioacchino.delregno@collabora.com>
Signed-off-by: Alexandre Mergnat <amergnat@baylibre.com>
